{"tid":2220375,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴警將12歲少女壓在地上，警修改字眼由「制服」變「截停」","createTime":"2020-09-27T15:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T17:56:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b86f32faa11dbb5555f4e62fed9b243307285f70","tid":2220375,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AYhfjH4APznTwF_UKf.jcg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/19d6c946f985a64373174fa58a5f12ae\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAYhfjH4APznTwF_UKf.jcg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F19d6c946f985a64373174fa58a5f12ae&h=6924a7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/防暴警將12歲少女壓在地上-警修改字眼由-制服-變-截停-111932888.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%8712%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%93%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC%E7%94%B1-%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D-%E8%AE%8A-%E6%88%AA%E5%81%9C-111932888.html&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUhFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=0da4cbde\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/防暴警將12歲少女壓在地上-警修改字眼由-制服-變-截停-111932888.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUhFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=06028410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】在本月6日九龍出現警民衝突，一名12歲少女被多名防暴警員壓在地上，警方當日曾指行動是在由於該名少女形迹可疑，警方追截並將其「制服」。但警方今日(27日)回覆傳媒查詢時對該事件的描述有變。警方指該行動是警員以最低武力將該名少女「截停」，沒有再提及「制服」一事，並稱事後曾安慰少女。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆東網查詢時表示，本月6日下午約4時，警方在旺角西洋菜南街發現有近百人集結及叫囂，遂向人羣發出警告，要求他們離開。然而有部分人拒絕離開，繼續集結，警方於是截停搜查相關集結者。過程中一名少女拔足狂奔，警員「截停」該少女始知她只有12歲，在場警員馬上安排女警安慰及照顧其需要。<br />\n<br />\n但該名女童與現場其餘集結者涉嫌參與受禁羣組聚集，因此她被警方以違反《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例》票控。警方又強調重視保護兒童及青少年，亦非常關注有未成年人士逗留在有示威者集結、叫囂、及投擲雜物的街道上；但是，警方同時亦有責任保障所有市民大眾的安全。<br />\n<br />\n警方補充指，任何人士如認為於警方處理任何事件時受到不合理對待，可向投訴警察課作出投訴，投訴警察課會按既定程序公平公正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3qr.dsj8b5czKh6lsSvYPg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/0f1048b27ac6df2e276c1737aef52ccc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3qr.dsj8b5czKh6lsSvYPg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F0f1048b27ac6df2e276c1737aef52ccc&h=be99dd9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7fd8c6d68ba293b9f463dbbe7780596cd99d469","tid":2220375,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"有撚哂片都要死雞撐飯蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食屎啦死黑警"},{"pid":"c2acc895036abca5a85c3f3d34fb1792b8eed6a5","tid":2220375,"uid":378740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"抽水就抽水拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7507994088ead6ee34cf37fd492680db7b6120e1","tid":2220375,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2fdb1546863ff968537afb7346fe7eb12dd3a5","tid":2220375,"uid":187676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"「截停」都咁暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲啲使唔使「問話」都要揼兩鎚呀"},{"pid":"36a1e122f1581cc5f86a1227ff2c184d3aeb5e0b","tid":2220375,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:44:52.000Z",